name: BENE_MDCR_STUS_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE REASON FOR A BENEFICIARYS ENTITLEMENT TO MEDICARE BENEFITS.

name: BENE_MDCR_STUS_CD_DESC
comment: A DESCRIPTION OF A CODE IDENTIFYING THE REASON FOR A BENEFICIARYS ENTITLEMENT TO MEDICARE BENEFITS.

name: META_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND A 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT INITIALLY LOADED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_SRC_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) USED TO IDENTIFY THE SPECIFIC SOURCE OF THE DATA WHEN A ROW IS LOADED INTO THE IDR.    REFERENCE TABLE: V2_MDCR_META_DCTNRY_SRC

name: BENE_AGED_STUS_ID
comment: AN IDENTIFIER INDICATING WHETHER AGE IS A REASON FOR A BENEFICIARYS ENTITLEMENT TO MEDICARE.

name: BENE_AGED_STUS_DESC
comment: A DESCRIPTION OF AN IDENTIFIER INDICATING WHETHER AGE IS A REASON FOR A BENEFICIARYS ENTITLEMENT TO MEDICARE.

name: BENE_MDCR_STUS_GRP_CD
comment: NOT DEFINED, BECAUSE THE DATA FOR THIS COLUMN IS NOT PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE AND CONTAINS THE SAME VALUES AS THE BENE_MDCR_STUS_CD COLUMN.
